Mercy, come out.

198
00:24:20,626 --> 00:24:22,332
I be not mercy,

199
00:24:22,461 --> 00:24:26,420
I be the witch of the wood
and I have come to steal ye.

200
00:24:26,507 --> 00:24:29,419
Hear me stick
a-flying through the trees:

201
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:32,217
Clickety-clackity,
clickety-clackity!

202
00:24:32,304 --> 00:24:34,420
- Mercy!
- Clickety-clackity.

203
00:24:34,515 --> 00:24:35,925
Why is't when thou dost a wrong,

204
00:24:36,016 --> 00:24:38,098
I be a-washin father's clothes
like a slave,

205
00:24:38,185 --> 00:24:40,847
- and thou art playing idle?
- Because mother hates you.

206
00:24:40,938 --> 00:24:43,554
Spoilt child. I'll tell mother
you've left the farm alone.

207
00:24:43,649 --> 00:24:45,810
