210
00:24:49,571 --> 00:24:52,859
I could go to the brook
before you let the witch take Sam.

211
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:55,032
- Quiet, thee.
- It were a wolf stole Sam.

212
00:24:55,119 --> 00:24:58,361
