riding cloak, about the wood.

213
00:24:58,497 --> 00:25:01,159
- Father showed me the tracks.
- It was a witch.

214
00:25:01,250 --> 00:25:06,995
Aye, it was a witch,
mercy, you speak aright.

215
00:25:07,089 --> 00:25:08,670
- Thomasin!
- It was I.

216
00:25:08,757 --> 00:25:10,088
Liar.

217
00:25:10,175 --> 00:25:14,544
Twas I what stole him,
I be the witch of the wood.

218
00:25:14,638 --> 00:25:17,675
- Liar! Liar!
- I am.

219
00:25:17,766 --> 00:25:19,506
List not to her, mercy.

220
