If ever thou tellst thy mother of this,

235
00:25:59,933 --> 00:26:02,094
I'll witch thee and thy mother!
And Jonas too!

236
00:26:02,186 --> 00:26:04,142
- Caleb!
- Stop thy tears and swear by silence.

237
00:26:04,229 --> 00:26:06,390
I swear it.
You'll not tell mother nor father.

238
00:26:06,482 --> 00:26:09,064
- I swear.
- Thomasin! Let her alone.

239
00:26:09,151 --> 00:26:12,564
Get away from her, Caleb,
or she'll witch thee!

240
00:26:15,282 --> 00:26:18,319
